The AJAX call should be:

     $.ajax({
        type: &quot;POST&quot;,
        url: &quot;post.php&quot;,
        data: {pTableData: TableData},
        success: function(msg){
            alert(msg);
            // return value stored in msg variable
        } 
    });

Changed `data: &quot;pTableData=&quot; + TableData` to `{pTableData: TableData}`

